# Auto-generated provenance and output data (not source)
rectify/data/README.md
rectify/data/PROVENANCE.json
rectify/data/corrected_3ends.tsv
rectify/data/corrected_3ends_stats.tsv
rectify/data/corrected_3ends_index.bed.gz
